# MEMORY — append-only session and experience log

Cross-session log of what happened, what was tried, and what was
learned. This is the long-form companion to the `[LEARN]` SQLite DB:
where `[LEARN]` captures discrete rules, MEMORY captures the
narrative those rules emerged from.

Entry header convention:

```
## YYYY-MM-DD [tag]: one-line summary
```

Tags: `experiment`, `learning`, `pivot`, `failure`, `success`,
`paper`, `infra`.

